{"tid":886990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? IT人批評高層意見，慘遭當眾辱罵及掌摑，更要下跪道歉！","createTime":"2018-11-02T14:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T05:09:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"d127e91a8339b8d2016ee982030c9f1cdbd88e86","tid":886990,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T14:01:21.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】南韓一名科技公司主席三年前因不滿職員在網上撰寫批評，當眾辱罵及掌摑有關職員，更要求對方下跪道歉。事件最近才被揭發，引發輿論批評，警方已就事件立案調查。<br />\n<br />\n片中穿淺綠恤衫的公司高層梁振浩，大庭廣眾下掌摑男職員，又要求他下跪道歉。這段打人實況，星期二最先由南韓獨立網媒《打破新聞》公開，但其實事件早在2015年4月發生。<br />\n<br />\n起因是穿黑衣的<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊科技開發人員</span>，在公司網頁留言區寫了批評高層的意見，梁振浩找到「寫手」後就開始教訓。梁振浩還要求另一名職員錄下打人過程，稱要留為紀念，被打的男職員已經離職。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xaz2uL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xaz2uL.jpg&h=04cdc21d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=325899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D325899&d=XjQgjJGG3Jmbsj%2FlSM8MSC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7d451d72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D325899&h=7f311ac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=325899</a>"},{"pid":"ec5d123db2fb98d86cc0f4ee572f9120585412d1","tid":886990,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"片 :<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=10&amp;v=cdqh9fMm9Ec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D10%26v%3Dcdqh9fMm9Ec&d=XjQgjJGG3Jmbsj%2FlSM8MSC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=721d4d9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=10&amp;v=cdqh9fMm9Ec</a>"},{"pid":"7e1f5987a52fc0c0841d6207d02016d0e98c395c","tid":886990,"uid":19454,"like":